{"tid":2438400,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[廚具分享會] 魚鏟 fish spatula","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T16:39:36.000Z","uid":182683,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e220de6cf857cdd69c16f6c9fb07ca498d6cf3ba","tid":2438400,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"法國香港好似冇咩人用呢支野 fish spatula<br />\n唔知點解叫魚鏟 我反咩都用佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dG4Mkh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdG4Mkh9.png&h=2361e6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家買個時 一定要係不鏽鋼 記得要買夠薄身同埋可以屈既 咁先反到任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於個手柄位就自己鍾意 但成舊不鏽鋼有個好處就係可以係洗碗機用 木/膠手柄用耐左會爆開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CmKRp5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CmKRp5.png&h=b88b7555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2M2ibp9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2M2ibp9.png&h=f48292e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於易潔鑊用到既 我暫時都未搵到有岩用既fish spatula 所以用住矽膠先 雖然唔夠厚 但起碼屈到同唔會溶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MU0onwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMU0onwZ.png&h=82ca9e25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKi1TDH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKi1TDH.png&h=3dc8c635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千其唔好用尼龍(nylon)質地 就算寫住耐熱250c我都用過 大火少少就溶 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fBbwqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fBbwqK.png&h=e3b68ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTmVX5N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTmVX5N.png&h=4774e199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我ig有片煎蛋示範好用個幾支點好用法 <br />\n有興趣可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=e1bac639\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a>"},{"pid":"df8336f7011bc19911d41d594dca0141b592c5fb","tid":2438400,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"冇台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c12124f56cca75fab3add0773318843db0b3a2","tid":2438400,"uid":384534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"香港人有鑊鏟 點解要買魚鏟？"},{"pid":"c25de1d1c3d053cd3bd0654aeb29a9e6e6b13ab4","tid":2438400,"uid":182683,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47c12124f56cca75fab3add0773318843db0b3a2","tid":2438400,"uid":384534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"香港人有鑊鏟 點解要買魚鏟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"因為唔同用法 一黎唔夠薄 二黎冇啲窿窿可以隔走啲油 同埋面積唔夠大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82c8d24da46643d9a7417243de6073878da0451","tid":2438400,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8336f7011bc19911d41d594dca0141b592c5fb","tid":2438400,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"冇台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"台妹都用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9380c4c0d37e61ce83369dd200baccb099eae4","tid":2438400,"uid":384534,"like":0,"di