-Clad哥款會好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd849ccd6a6a46d5942b02dc6754e385ac894032","tid":2438400,"uid":182683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d24091cdc949bf4093997bbf1a39344281757a1b","tid":2438400,"uid":137316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"想知食鬼點睇All-Clad不鏽鋼哥款fish spatula<br />\n一支平嘅好用啲定All-Clad哥款會好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"我自己排名：吉川(第一張圖右邊)&gt;victorinox&gt;柳宗理<br />\n我自己用緊victorinox 超薄勁好用同埋木柄幾好 made in use好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAll-clad有支係全不鏽鋼應該都唔錯 但會角道唔同一般fish spatula 唔係個個岩用<br />\nAll-clad另外膠手柄個支我自己麻麻 有時煮野食行開左 放左係到會溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得最好係我張圖右邊個款 日本買 好似係吉川 <br />\n唔算超薄但係成塊一體成形 應該可以用成世 <br />\n仲有把係柳宗理出既 個鏟位都係超薄好好用 不過就唔係成塊過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5y5r8E0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5y5r8E0.jpg&h=078295b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a40cd71647c20c31ac8914ce21dd8d2f40495c61","tid":2438400,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:29:06.000Z","msg":"呢隻嘢最適合用嚟移動一啲易散/變形嘅嘢<br />\n例如煎太陽蛋 煎魚 或者新鮮出爐嘅曲奇餅"},{"pid":"baed0a93581ff5f939e754a96528c0441dc55aa2","tid":2438400,"uid":326470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"呢d周圍都買到，翻蛋都好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa9f255ea9d16e4224d2a81ffef844026462dbe","tid":2438400,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a40cd71647c20c31ac8914ce21dd8d2f40495c61","tid":2438400,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:29:06.000Z